{"selectedVerses":[{"reference":{"book":"Esther","chapter":8,"verse":1},"text":"On that day King Ahasuerus gave to Queen Esther the house of Haman, the enemy of the Jews. And Mordecai came before the king, for Esther had told what he was to her."},{"reference":{"book":"Esther","chapter":8,"verse":7},"text":"Then King Ahasuerus said to Queen Esther and to Mordecai the Jew, \u0022Behold, I have given Esther the house of Haman, and they have hanged him on the gallows, because he intended to lay hands on the Jews."},{"reference":{"book":"Esther","chapter":9,"verse":13},"text":"And Esther said, \u0022If it please the king, let the Jews who are in Susa be allowed tomorrow also to do according to this day\u0027s edict. And let the ten sons of Haman be hanged on the gallows.\u0022"},{"reference":{"book":"Esther","chapter":6,"verse":14},"text":"While they were yet talking with him, the king\u0027s eunuchs arrived and hurried to bring Haman to the feast that Esther had prepared."},{"reference":{"book":"Esther","chapter":5,"verse":9},"text":"And Haman went out that day joyful and glad of heart. But when Haman saw Mordecai in the king\u0027s gate, that he neither rose nor trembled before him, he was filled with wrath against Mordecai."}],"allVerseReferences":[{"book":"Esther","chapter":4,"verse":7},{"book":"Esther","chapter":5,"verse":4},{"book":"Esther","chapter":5,"verse":5},{"book":"Esther","chapter":5,"verse":8},{"book":"Esther","chapter":5,"verse":9},{"book":"Esther","chapter":5,"verse":10},{"book":"Esther","chapter":5,"verse":11},{"book":"Esther","chapter":5,"verse":12},{"book":"Esther","chapter":5,"verse":14},{"book":"Esther","chapter":9,"verse":10},{"book":"Esther","chapter":9,"verse":12},{"book":"Esther","chapter":9,"verse":13},{"book":"Esther","chapter":6,"verse":4},{"book":"Esther","chapter":9,"verse":14},{"book":"Esther","chapter":6,"verse":5},{"book":"Esther","chapter":6,"verse":6},{"book":"Esther","chapter":6,"verse":7},{"book":"Esther","chapter":6,"verse":10},{"b